---
const testimonials = [
  {
    quote:
      "Steph brings a refreshing blend of professionalism and personality to every piece she has written for ConvertKit. She knows the online marketing space back-to-front—each piece she writes is rooted in data, and she takes the initiative to reach out to sources and subject matter experts to bring each piece to life. Steph delivers every piece on (or sometimes well before!) her deadlines, her drafts require little to no editing, and she always takes feedback into account on subsequent articles. Each piece only gets better and better—it's no wonder she holds the byline on the most visited post on the ConvertKit blog. If you have the chance, I would recommend adding Steph to your writing roster in a heartbeat.",
    name: 'Kieran',
    role: 'ConvertKit',
  },
  {
    quote:
      "Stephanie is a fantastic writer and a pleasure to work with: she's flexible, knowledgeable, and is happy to interview subject matter experts and dig into research projects to ensure the content she delivers is expertly written. I appreciate how Stephanie approaches the editorial process with an open mind and that she gracefully accepts and provides feedback where needed. I would recommend and trust Stephanie for any writing project and am looking forward to partnering with her again in the future.",
    name: 'Tawni',
    role: 'Hotjar',
  },
];
---
<section id="testimonials" class="section testimonials">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">What clients say</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Trusted by the teams she writes for</h2>
    <div class="testimonials__grid">
      {testimonials.map((t) => (
        <figure class="quote">
          <blockquote class="quote__text">{t.quote}</blockquote>
          <figcaption class="quote__by">
            <span class="quote__name">{t.name}</span>
            <span class="quote__role">{t.role}</span>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials {
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border-block: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .testimonials__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    margin-top: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  }

  .quote {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.75rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .quote__text {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.4rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .quote__by {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
  }

  .quote__name {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .quote__role {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 780px) {
    .testimonials__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
